reviewText: This probably does not do justice to these events.  But ... it is as close as maybe.  Good musicians, one heck of a lot more comfortable than being there.
Title: Austin City Limits Music Festival 2005

reviewText: This Was an okay movie. it had some good artist. butt all in all it was okay. this is one of those movies that you watch if nothing else is on i'd rather listen to the cd instead. if you have not watched this movie then i recommend you do/or don't
Title: Austin City Limits Music Festival 2005

reviewText: Lot's of samplers from startup bands. Mostly daytime (small unknown bands). Disjointed concert DVD. The Bonus disk is a joke. Get Austin City 2004 instead.
Title: Austin City Limits Music Festival 2005

reviewText: Excellent DVD, great lineup and great video and sound. A real nice cross-section of performers. Highlights include Gov't Mule, Eisley, Decemberists, Widespread Panic, and many, many more. Thanks for all the hard work.
Title: Austin City Limits Music Festival 2005

reviewText: This music compilation is a little :harder" than what I expected.I was hoping for more subdued performances.Worth a look, though.
Title: Austin City Limits Music Festival 2005
